Program: Discovery
Title: In search of Muziris
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz5m
Last Broadcast Date: 02 May 2006
The programme goes in search of Muziris, a mythical south Indian port. Archaeologists are searching for a former Roman port, all trace of it was thought to have vanished, however recent discoveries would suggest there may be some remains still on its former site.